  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Star Wars: Jedi Power Battles follows the story of Episode I: The Phantom Menace. The Game Boy Advance port featured 3 playable characters as opposed to 5 on the PS1 and Dreamcast, with only Obi-Wan, Qui-Gon, and Mace Windu being playable. The game alternates between an isometric view and side-scrolling.",
